ğŸ Steps to Run
SQL:

Create FishStoreDB in Azure SQL.

Run schema.sql.

Backend:

Set up with your Azure SQL credentials in db.js.

Run npm install and npm start.

Frontend:

Use Next.js or React.

Point API requests to the backend.

Run npm install and npm run dev.
